arts.ttl: Groningen Ease to Victory over Sorry Heracles
arts.sum: Groningen eased to a comfortable 4-0 victory over Heracles Almelo on Friday evening. The home side were ahead within the first ten minutes with Brynjólfur Willumsson finding the net with a powerful strike.
